            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "); that the matter was not to be lightly decided.",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "(21) Eye for eye, tooth for tooth.—This is to be effected by the award of the judges, not as a matter of private revenge. But manifestly it rests with the injured party to press the case.",
